methods.applicationFieldToBytes:
Convenience method to create the flight ticket bytes for the application field.

:param applicationId: (java.lang.String) - the application ID
:param fieldName: (java.lang.String) - the field name
:return: (byte[]) the ticket bytes
methods.applicationFieldToPath:
Convenience method to create the flight descriptor path for the application field.

:param applicationId: (java.lang.String) - the application ID
:param fieldName: (java.lang.String) - the field name
:return: (java.util.List<java.lang.String>) the path
